  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Although the workload is getting heavier in many professions]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[and physical and psychological wear on personnel is steadily increasing,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[the statutory retirement age should in the future not remain at 63 years.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[For,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[due to the low birth rate,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[the proportion of the elderly population and with it pension costs are on the rise,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[and furthermore,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[due to today's healthcare]]></edu>
  <edu id="e9"><![CDATA[most people in many occupations are fitter for work in old age than before.]]></edu>
